title: Warum ist Wukong anders? Reliktschild + Klone Interaktionen

embed.description: 8.12 Why is Wukong different? Relic Clones | League of Why #002 Happened to find this out in one of my recent ranked games and hopped into customs/practice tool to test it out. Wukong is the only of the "Clone"-Champions capable of duping gold.
